Package ohha.puzzlecrafter.auxiliary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IsDuplicated
    Provides a slew of static methods for testing whether a cell's value is unique in its row, column or region.
    Neighbours
    Provides a slew of methods to quickly access the neighbouring cells of a given cell.
    SingleTimeEntryQueue<T>
    Represents a queue into which elements may be entered only once, regardless of whether they've already exited the queue or not.
